ful to the guild, as well as not recruiting people that need other things than we can offer. We can not schedule the guilds activities around the need for people to level. We can not schedule the guilds activities around getting epics for new members and we can not recruit people that have no chance of surviving encounters with high level AoE mobs. <br>
<br>
New recruits need <br>
- Resists: Mr/Fr/Cr over 100 simultaneously and Mr/Dr/Pr over 100 simultaneously <br>
- Faction: Non KoS CoV faction. Must be willing to keep the faction the guild chooses to follow at any given time. <br>
- Epics: New recruits can not expect the guild to make a special effort obtaining their epics. <br>
- Playtime: While people are not expected to let their RL suffer because they need to log in to attend a raid, they are expected to show up to raids when they are online. <br>
- EB item<br>
- Instant right-click buff item that works indoors (8th Coldain ring, SGE etc)<br>
